title: BRIEF-Ymagis H1 net income rises by 28.6 pct to 0.9 million euros
text:
BRIEF-Ymagis H1 net income rises by 28.6 pct to 0.9 million euros Sept 23 
Sept 23 Ymagis SA : 
* Reports H1 net income group share of 0.9 million euros versus 0.7 million euros a year ago 
* H1 EBITDA is 26.2 million versus 24.3 million euros a year ago Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
